✔ Optional.of(value)                → Throws an exception if the value is null.
✔ Optional.ofNullable(value)        → Allows null values.
✔ orElse(defaultValue)              → Returns a default value if Optional is empty.
✔ orElseThrow(exception)            → Throws an exception if Optional is empty.
✔ map(Function)                     → Transforms values inside Optional.
✔ filter(Predicate)                 → Filters based on conditions.
✔ flatMap(Function)                 → Chains multiple Optional values.